title: Iron sharpens iron.

author: Russell Brand
description:
Thicker, Fuller Hair Starts with ROOTS! Click www.twc.health/BRAND and use code BRAND for 10% Off + Free Shipping on every order.

Boiling dead bodies in a steel vat and flushing them down the drain is now being sold as an eco-friendly funeral. I unpack the rise of “alkaline hydrolysis”—marketed with phrases like “gentle heat” and “green burials”—and why it signals more than just a change in funeral tech. It’s the commodification of death itself, another step toward a world stripped of ritual, meaning, and the sacred. Don’t let them tell you this is just about the environment—it’s about your soul.
